x4freetext: Two 240Pu samples were used. The samples were of a
Pu-Al alloy, ~1.2% of Al by weight,sealed in Al cans.
The weight of Pu was about 97%, giving a thickness of
capture and 20 nsecs for transmission measurements.
Correction for multiple scattering in capture data
using a Monte Carlo code. Also correction for dead-time
